transformeR 0.0-2
=================

* New function `persistence`, for lagged autocorrelation climatological grid creation 
* New function `PC2grid`, for conversion of a principal component into a time-series grid
* New function `grid2raster`, for grid to 'raster' class conversion
* New util function `bindGrid.member`, for grid binding across member dimension
* New internal utility `clim2sgdf` for flexible conversion between climatological grids and SpatialGridDataFrame-class objects
* Other minor changes, code efficiency improvements and documentation updates



